*Bolji* izbor je na kraju donio. (He made a better choice in the end.)

Njegov *bolji* drugar je zavoleo devojku. (His better friend fell in love with the girl.)

Mnogo *boljih* stvari želim da postignem. (I want to achieve much better things.)

Ona je radila *bolje* od mene. (She worked better than me.)

*Bolje* je biti pažljiv. (It is better to be careful.)